entries.title_d: The Dantooine station has hired you to pick up a micro-processor from a shipping company in Corellia. The company will not deliver out to Dantooine and that processor is desperately needed.
entries.title: Corellia System: Pickup the Micro-Processor
entries.split_quest_alert: Travel to the Tatooine system. A freighter that was supposed to deliver Lemdurion Plates to the Dantooine system has been delayed and needs an escort through the system.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the arrival location of the freighter and wait for them to arrive.
entries.quest_location_d: The shipping company has agreed to drop the cargo onto your ship as long as you meet them in Corellia.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with the freighter and transfer it to your vessel.
entries.hello_d: Ok, let's make this fast. Dock when ready and I will transfer the goods.
entries.found_loc_d: The shipping company has agreed to meet you at the supplied location.
entries.failed_destroyed: We needed that cargo. Where are we going to get another one now?
entries.docking_started_delivery: Transferring cargo to your vessel now. Stand by.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Ok, you have the micro-processor. See you around.
entries.arrived_at_delivery: Stand by for arrival of the freighter carrying our cargo.
